parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate when braking, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when stopping at intersections or on highways.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders or stalls when braking
hesitates when shifting gears
makes a clunking or grinding noise
and may exhibit a sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate when shifting gears, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when stopping at intersections or on highways.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders or stalls when shifting gears
hesitates when accelerating
makes a whining or grinding noise
and may exhibit a sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate when shifting gears, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when stopping at intersections or on highways.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates when shifting gears
hesitates when accelerating
makes a clicking or grinding noise
and may exhibit a sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to repair or replace the Takata airbags in a timely manner can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or may rupture, causing harm to occupants.
symptoms: No symptoms are reported
but owners are experiencing frustration and concern due to the delay in repairing or replacing the airbags.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor system can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of an accident, which can cause serious injury or death to the passenger.
symptoms: The passenger airbag warning light fails to turn on or turns off intermittently
even when an adult is seated in the passenger seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death to the occupants.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in the event of an accident
even when the vehicle is traveling at a moderate speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the steering wheel to shake or vibrate, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel shakes or vibrates
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel feels loose or unresponsive
the vehicle wanders or drifts on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes hard to turn
the power steering pump fails
the hydraulic line corrodes or breaks
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the subframe can cause the vehicle to lose steering and braking ability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The subframe corrodes
the vehicle's steering and braking ability are affected
the vehicle's structural integrity is compromised.
